videos.description: West Virginia's Justin Crawford runs 38 yards to the Mountaineers 41.
videos.headline: Crawford breaks through for 38-yard run

videos.description: Will Grier is sacked by Ben Banogu to push the Mountaineers back to the 50-yard line.
videos.headline: TCU's Banogu crushes Grier for 8-yard loss

videos.description: John Diarse punctuates a great catch by shrugging off his defender to extend a Horned Frogs field-goal drive.
videos.headline: TCU's Diarse makes impressive grab around defender

videos.description: Kenny Hill finds Jalen Reagor down the sideline for a touchdown to extend the Horned Frogs' lead.
videos.headline: Reagor's 45-yard TD pads TCU's lead

videos.description: Will Grier connects with David Sill V for 64 yards to score late in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Sills closes gap on TCU with 64-yard TD

videos.description: West Virginia's Will Grier finds Ka'Raun White for a touchdown to tie TCU.
videos.headline: White's 76-yard TD ties it up

videos.description: KaVontae Turpin throws back to QB Kenny Hill, who takes it down the sideline for a 48-yard touchdown to put the Horned Frogs back ahead.
videos.headline: Trick play puts TCU back in the lead

videos.description: Will Grier finds David Sills V in the end zone to tie TCU in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Sills' second TD of the day ties the game

videos.description: TCU QB Kenny Hill scores three different ways Saturday, propelling the Horned Frogs to a victory over West Virginia.
